 for the Einstein constraints are\napparently the first such results that do not require smallness conditions on\nspatial derivatives of the mean extrinsic curvature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Feb 2008 18:10:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Feb 2008 19:29:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 12 Apr 2008 09:10:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-01-13"}
