\\th_i\\}_{i=0}^d$ and $\\{\\th^*_i\\}_{i=0}^d$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Feb 2008 05:38:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-02-11"}
